==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undershot
<hw>Un"der*shot`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Having the lower incisor teeth projecting beyond
the upper ones, as in the bulldog.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Moved by water passing beneath; -- said of a water
wheel, and opposed to <xex>overshot</xex>; <as>as, an <ex>undershot</ex>
wheel</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undershrievalty</ent>⟦br⟧
